4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to help individuals become proficient in JavaScript and Python within 18 weeks. Participants will gain hands-on experience by coding in key web development languages, learning algorithm scripting, and utilizing APIs to create functional applications. The program features 16 weeks of classes plus 2 weeks for a final project, with three classes per week and a low student-to-instructor ratio of 7:1. No prior coding or advanced math skills are necessary, and courses are available in English and Spanish. Graduates receive a Full-Stack Developer certificate. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop